categories: Category:Imperial Navy officers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: Masil Veit was a human male lieutenant who served as a communications officer in the Galactic Empire aboard the Executor-class Star Dreadnought Executor. In 3 ABY Veit contacted the Trandoshan bounty hunter Bossk and informed him of a bounty that had been placed for the capture of the Millennium Falcon by Darth Vader.
